This is a copyright license only. No patent rights are granted.
Any patent rights to inventions, methods, or designs embodied in
this code are expressly retained by the author.

## 四、无技术支持义务 / 4. No Support Obligation

作者无义务为使用者提供技术支持、代码维护、Bug 修复或版本更新。
本仓库 Issues 功能可能随时关闭。

The author has no obligation to provide technical support,
code maintenance, bug fixes, or version updates.

## 五、硬件安全声明 / 5. Hardware Safety

FPGA / 数字电路代码的错误可能导致：
- 时序违例引起系统不稳定
- 过流 / 过热导致硬件物理损坏
- 数据丢失或损坏

使用者自行承担全部风险。作者不对因使用本代码造成的任何
硬件损坏、数据丢失、财产损失负责。

Errors in FPGA/digital circuit code may cause system instability,
physical hardware damage, or data loss. Use entirely at your own risk.
The author assumes no liability for any damages.

